sequenceDiagram
  participant Operator
  participant CLI as CLI or Web API
  participant Service as Mission Service
  participant Harness as Runtime Harness
  participant Provider as Provider Registry
  participant Store as Local Store

  Operator->>CLI: create/run mission
  CLI->>Service: createMission or runMission
  Service->>Store: save workspace, mission, session metadata
  Service->>Harness: start session and agent runs
  Harness->>Provider: execute role prompt through selected provider
  Provider-->>Harness: structured role output or provider failure
  Harness->>Store: persist agent run, approval, artifact evidence
  Service-->>CLI: mission result, provider summary, action/approval state
  CLI-->>Operator: output, follow-up, evidence path
